OL,5, An ex-BBC director general has said he 
OL,6, does not think chairman Richard Sharp's
OL,7, "appointment should stand" because he  
OL,8, was an "unsuitable candidate" and the  
OL,9, process was "fatally flawed".          
OL,11,FMr Sharp is facing pressure over his   
OL,12,Frole in facilitating an #800,000 loan  
OL,13,Ffor then-prime minister Boris Johnson. 
OL,15,FJohn Birt, who was director general    
OL,16,Ffrom 1992 to 2000, said the "cosiness" 
OL,17,Fof the arrangement made him unsuitable.
OL,19,FMr Sharp's appointment is being        
OL,20,Finvestigated. He denies any wrongdoing.
